        <!-- HERO -->
        <section id="hero" class="flex flex-col items-start p-6 rounded-sm shadow-md hover:border-green-400 border-4 border-zinc-900 transition">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold underline text-white">
                Hi, I'm Alex!
            </h1>
            <h1 class="text-2xl text-white">
                DevOps & Infrastructure Engineer
            </h1>
            <p class="text-white mt-2">
                IT professional with a background in application development and a deep passion for infrastructure, DevOps, and automation. Currently working as a System Engineer, I focus on building reliable, scalable platforms through Infrastructure as Code, containerization, and modern DevOps practices. I'm also exploring AI-driven tooling to accelerate and simplify operational workflows.
            </p>
        </section>

