        <!-- ABOUT ME -->
        <section id="about" class="flex flex-col p-6 rounded-sm shadow-md hover:border-green-400 border-4 border-zinc-900 transition scroll-reveal">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white hover:underline decoration-wavy">About Me</h2>
            <p class="text-white">
                I'm an IT professional with experience spanning software development, infrastructure engineering, DevOps, and database administration. My career started in banking as an Application Developer building enterprise workflows on the Pega Platform and C# .NET synchronization services.
            </p>
            <p class="text-white mt-2">
                Over time, my focus shifted toward infrastructure and operations. I dove deep into Linux administration, containerization, Kubernetes, automation with Ansible, and modern DevOps practices. Today, as a System Engineer at Fortress Digital Services, I work on building reliable, scalable platforms and streamlining operational workflows.
            </p>
            <p class="text-white mt-2">
                I'm passionate about simplifying complex operations through automation and Infrastructure as Code. I'm also actively exploring AI-driven tooling to accelerate and improve how we build and manage infrastructure.
            </p>
        </section>

